task.summary: Create a servo-feedback implementation for a standard motor
Create a self-contained servo class (servo similar to the quater-scale ones connected to TETRIX controllers), and a supporting class for describing positions tied with slew rates
Create some classes to describe motion planner goals and sensing. More to come, before algorithms can be written.
Create a drivetrain, obstable sensor, relative position, helper exceptions
